item.title: Zachary Baker
item.description: I am a junior at Thomas Jefferson High School for Science and Technology in Northern Virginia. Some things I like to do include crew, coding, and playing chess. This site is my portion of the internet. It contains projects, my resume, the occasional blog post, and more. This site was made using Markdown as the main language and Hugo as a framework for building the site. I also used VSCode and Vim to edit all of the source files.
